 from negative infinity to x is negative 1, and from x is  negative 1 \+
to positive 3." }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 83 "The critical po
ints of the function are -1 and 3, these are where the slopes are 0." 
}}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
